I wanted to ask if you could share this go fund me link gf.me/639t . It’s not for me it’s for my momma. My sister died in a car accident the 15th of this month and I’m trying to help my momma out. She can’t work under this condition and I can’t afford to help her keep her house. So I’m just asking everyone if they could share and who ever wants to donate I’d highly appreciate it. I want my mom to keep the house my sister lived in. So she can keep my sister close even if she’s gone. Thank you for reading this and I love you for being so kind and sweet.
